title: NFL Week 1 Recap Podcast (Football 09/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner to break down week 1 of the 2018 NFL season. How are Bears fans holding up? Is Patrick Mahomes an MVP candidate? Should 49ers fans be worried about Jimmy Garoppolo? Are the Ravens for real? Who is to blame for the Steelers and Browns tie? All those questions answered plus much, much more.
